fields.Title: CARGO / NIGHT WATCHMAN BOOTH
fields.Description: René's booth dialogue shall be in here

fields.Title: Nightwatchman's Booth: "The drawers are empty save for old..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The drawers are empty save for old time sheets and receipts. One small box, however, does hold some cheap painkillers. They are slightly out of date.

fields.Title: Nightwatchman's Booth: "Nothing incriminating catches your..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Nothing incriminating catches your eye. The cabinets are clean and their sparse contents meticulously organized. There's a framed photograph on the table.

fields.Title: You: ""It's something to remember him by.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "It's something to remember him by."

fields.Title: Nightwatchman's Booth: "This is the nightwatchman's booth...."
fields.Dialogue Text: This is the nightwatchman's booth. The name on the door reads *René Arnoux*. A colourful uniform lies neatly folded on the table.

fields.Title: Empathy: "René looks like he's about to smile..."
fields.Dialogue Text: René looks like he's about to smile. This photo must be tied to some good memories.

fields.Title: Nightwatchman's Booth: "Oh boy, where to start. Elevated ri..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Oh boy, where to start. Elevated risk of dementia? Mini-strokes? Prophet's disease? Sudden death? Hair death? Erectile malfunction? Critical flatulence? Watery blood? Black mucous? Uncontrollable weeping? Increased sensitivity to l'Opéra? Inoperable joint disorder? Total spinal collapse?

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: "The lieutenant shrugs. "I'm not her..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The lieutenant shrugs. "I'm not here to tell you what to do, detective."

fields.Title: Savoir Faire: "Looks like the inhabitant is rather..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Looks like the inhabitant is rather pedantic when it comes to order.

fields.Title: Empathy: "The young man looks happy as well...."
fields.Dialogue Text: The young man looks happy as well. He's about to smile, right after this moment frozen in time. You're sure of that.

fields.Title: You: "Have a seat. Rest."
fields.Dialogue Text: Have a seat. Rest.

fields.Title: You: "Breathe deep."
fields.Dialogue Text: Breathe deep.

fields.Title: Nightwatchman's Booth: "You stand and exit the booth."
fields.Dialogue Text: You stand and exit the booth.

fields.Title: Nightwatchman's Booth: "You stand and exit the booth."
fields.Dialogue Text: You stand and exit the booth.

fields.Title: Savoir Faire: "Looks like the inhabitant was rathe..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Looks like the inhabitant was rather pedantic when it came to order.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""You really took an interest in tha..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You really took an interest in that old soldier." The lieutenant sounds surprised. "I guess there's no harm taking the picture. The dockworkers would probably throw it in the trash anyway."

fields.Title: You: "I don't see what the big deal is. T..."
fields.Dialogue Text: I don't see what the big deal is. This sounds pretty normal to me.

fields.Title: You: "I'm a cop. I have cop things to do...."
fields.Dialogue Text: I'm a cop. I have cop things to do. Murders to solve. People to help. Kim's counting on me.

fields.Title: Nightwatchman's Booth: "This is the nightwatchman's booth...."
fields.Dialogue Text: This is the nightwatchman's booth. The name on the door reads *René Arnoux*. René left his uniform neatly folded on the table.

fields.Title: Nightwatchman's Booth: "Nothing incriminating catches your..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Nothing incriminating catches your eye. The cabinets are clean and their sparse contents meticulously organized. Apart from the uniform, the only noteworthy item is a framed photograph on the table.

fields.Title: Nightwatchman's Booth: "As you take the colourful uniform,..."
fields.Dialogue Text: As you take the colourful uniform, a few cookie crumbs fall to the floor. The owner must have a sweet tooth.
fields.Alternate1: As you take the colourful uniform, a few cookie crumbs fall to the floor. René must have had a sweet tooth.
fields.Alternate2: As you take the colourful uniform, a few cookie crumbs fall to the floor. René must have a sweet tooth.

fields.Title: Nightwatchman's Booth: "It's a black and white photo of a y..."
fields.Dialogue Text: It's a black and white photo of a young couple out in a street fair. The man -- René -- is dressed in a Royal Carabineer uniform. The girl is young and very pretty. She is smiling playfully at the camera.

fields.Title: You: ""I'm gonna ask him about it.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "I'm gonna ask him about it."

fields.Title: Volition: "Listen... It's okay to take a few m..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Listen... It's okay to take a few minutes to yourself. Sit down and have a breather.

fields.Title: You: "Disco. Mirror balls. Kick-ass moves..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Disco. Mirror balls. Kick-ass moves. Boogie beat.

fields.Title: Nightwatchman's Booth: "This is the nightwatchman's booth...."
fields.Dialogue Text: This is the nightwatchman's booth. The name on the door reads *René Arnoux*.

fields.Title: You: "Maybe René is hiding something inte..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Maybe René is hiding something interesting here. (Search the booth.)

dialogueEntries.conditionsString: IsKimHere() == false  and  Variable["plaza.met_rene"] == true  and  Variable["cargo.guardbooth_took_the_picture"] == false

fields.Title: You: "[Leave.]"
fields.Dialogue Text: [Leave.]

fields.Title: Endurance: "You need to rest. Your body is achi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You need to rest. Your body is aching. Getting in here has taken something out of you. Have a seat.

fields.Title: You: "Get up."
fields.Dialogue Text: Get up.

fields.Title: Nightwatchman's Booth: "Maybe this was a bad idea..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Maybe this was a bad idea...

fields.Title: Nightwatchman's Booth: "Yes. Moving along."
fields.Dialogue Text: Yes. Moving along.

fields.Title: Nightwatchman's Booth: "The photo remains neatly placed on..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The photo remains neatly placed on the edge of the table.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Why did you take that?" the lieute..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Why did you take that?" the lieutenant asks, glancing at the photo.
fields.Alternate1: "Why did you take that picture of René?" the lieutenant asks, glancing at the photo.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""I don't know about stealing people..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I don't know about stealing people's *very colourful* clothes like that..." He looks on disapprovingly.

fields.Title: You: ""This is gonna take my shit to the..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "This is gonna take my shit to the next level."

fields.Title: Reaction Speed: "Don't think about that! Quick, thin..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Don't think about that! Quick, think about something else!

fields.Title: You: "... oh my God, I went up to a woman..."
fields.Dialogue Text: ... oh my God, I went up to a woman and actually said *I want to have fuck with you* earlier. What the hell is wrong with me?

fields.Title: You: "Get up."
fields.Dialogue Text: Get up.

fields.Title: You: ""Kim, I'm gonna take a quick look i..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Kim, I'm gonna take a quick look inside." (Search the booth.)

dialogueEntries.conditionsString: IsKimHere()  and  Variable["plaza.met_rene"] == false  and  Variable["cargo.guardbooth_took_the_picture"] == false

fields.Title: You: "Search for a little something-somet..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Search for a little something-something to help you out.

fields.Title: You: "Let's see what the nightwatchman ke..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Let's see what the nightwatchman keeps in here. (Search the booth.)

dialogueEntries.conditionsString: IsKimHere() == false  and  Variable["plaza.met_rene"] == false  and  Variable["cargo.guardbooth_took_the_picture"] == false

fields.Title: You: ""I'm making an artistic photo colla..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I'm making an artistic photo collage, Kim."

fields.Title: Nightwatchman's Booth: "You take the painkillers. They are..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You take the painkillers. They are yours now.

fields.Title: You: "Moving along!"
fields.Dialogue Text: Moving along!

fields.Title: You: ""So this is where René works. I'm g..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "So this is where René works. I'm gonna look around." (Search the booth.)
fields.Alternate1: "So this is where René worked. I'm gonna look around." (Search the booth.)

dialogueEntries.conditionsString: IsKimHere()  and  Variable["plaza.met_rene"] == true  and  Variable["cargo.guardbooth_took_the_picture"] == false

fields.Title: You: "Leave the picture alone."
fields.Dialogue Text: Leave the picture alone.

fields.Title: You: "Take the painkillers."
fields.Dialogue Text: Take the painkillers.

fields.Title: Nightwatchman's Booth: "Stale air floods through your nostr..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Stale air floods through your nostrils. Not a single mote of dust floats inside your lungs, though. The inside of the booth is immaculate.

fields.Title: You: ""I'm done here.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "I'm done here."

fields.Title: Nightwatchman's Booth: "Nothing incriminating catches your..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Nothing incriminating catches your eye. The cabinets are clean and their sparse contents meticulously organized. There's a framed photograph on the table.

fields.Title: Nightwatchman's Booth: "It's a black and white photo of a y..."
fields.Dialogue Text: It's a black and white photo of a young couple out in a street fair. The man is young, dark-skinned, and dressed in a Royal Carabineer uniform. The girl is smiling playfully at the camera.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Let's get going," the lieutenant s..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Let's get going," the lieutenant says impatiently. "The entire neighbourhood can see us up here."

fields.Title: You: ""Kim, would you mind if I helped my..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Kim, would you mind if I helped myself to some meds?"

fields.Title: You: "I hope I'm not fucking René over by..."
fields.Dialogue Text: I hope I'm not fucking René over by taking his painkillers.

fields.Title: You: "I am scared I will never be held or..."
fields.Dialogue Text: I am scared I will never be held or loved in this world again.

fields.Title: Nightwatchman's Booth: "Your nihilistic humour renders the..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Your nihilistic humour renders the list of side-effects null and void. Just like everything else in this empty world.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""If you must." The lieutenant looks..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "If you must." The lieutenant looks around. "But please hurry -- we're pretty easy to spot up here."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""I suppose René is not going to be..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I suppose René is not going to be needing it anymore." He studies the uniform. "It's a bit too colourful for my taste, though."

fields.Title: You: ""It's, uhm, needed for work and all..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "It's, uhm, needed for work and all that."

fields.Title: Savoir Faire: "Take it. It's just there. Who cares..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Take it. It's just there. Who cares? It's not like anyone's gonna need it.

fields.Title: Nightwatchman's Booth: "The enormity of the case before you..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The enormity of the case before you dwarfs the list of side-effects. You can't even see the side-effects anymore. They're nothing to you.

fields.Title: You: "That's kind of sad, actually..."
fields.Dialogue Text: That's kind of sad, actually...

fields.Title: Nightwatchman's Booth: "This is the nightwatchman's booth...."
fields.Dialogue Text: This is the nightwatchman's booth. The name on the door reads *René Arnoux*.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Fine." He nods. "But let's move. I..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Fine." He nods. "But let's move. I don't want to be seen snooping around here."

fields.Title: Nightwatchman's Booth: "The chair is not as austere as the..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The chair is not as austere as the rest of the booth. A thin grey pillow is attached to the seat, secured to the stiles by black ribbons.

fields.Title: You: ""I'm a cop. It's instinctual to col..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I'm a cop. It's instinctual to collect evidence."

fields.Title: You: ""*Something* about this man peaks m..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "*Something* about this man peaks my interest. I think this can be a side-thing."

fields.Title: Authority: "Generally speaking, it would be *di..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Generally speaking, it would be *dishonourable* to take it. But then... it looks like a military uniform! And wearing that is very honourable. So, a conflict of honour. It's up to you.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""You're *really* interested in that..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You're *really* interested in that old soldier," he remarks, surprised. "Not sure I understand your fascination, but sure -- as long as it doesn't take up a whole lot of time."

fields.Title: You: "Read the side-effects."
fields.Dialogue Text: Read the side-effects.

fields.Title: Nightwatchman's Booth: "The imagined dazzle of light overwh..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The imagined dazzle of light overwhelms any list of potential side-effects. Any negative thoughts are drowned out by the fantastic blast of *disco*.

fields.Title: You: "Take the uniform."
fields.Dialogue Text: Take the uniform.

fields.Title: You: "Take the picture."
fields.Dialogue Text: Take the picture.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Of course you are," he says matter..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Of course you are," he says matter-of-factly. "What murder investigation would be complete without an arbitrary photo collage."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Fantastic. Try not to wear it with..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Fantastic. Try not to wear it with other similarly colourful clothes, okay?"
